/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [noncsd].[sprMilkGetSetData]    Script Date: 5/25/2022 1:04:30 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
-- =============================================
-- EXEC AFBL_Factory.noncsd.sprMilkGetSetData @vcCase='28', @vcParaFour = '2022-05-01', @vcParaFive = '2022-05-24'
-- =============================================
CREATE PROCEDURE [noncsd].[sprMilkGetSetData]
	@vcCase nvarchar(5), @vcParaTwo nvarchar(20) = null, @vcParaThree nvarchar(20) = null, @vcParaFour nvarchar(20) = null, @vcParaFive nvarchar(20) = null, 
	@vcParaSix nvarchar(20) = null,@vcParaSeven nvarchar(20) = null, @vcParaEight nvarchar(20) = null, @vcParaNine nvarchar(20) = null, 
	@vcParaTen nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaEleven nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaTwelve nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaThirteen nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaFourteen nvarchar(20)= null, 
	@vcParaFifteen nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaSixteen nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaSeventeen nvarchar(20)= null, @XML xml = null
	
	/* @vcCase varchar(5), @vcEnroll Varchar(12) = null, @vcPlantId varchar(12) = null, @vcMachineId varchar(12) = null, @vcUnqIdPro nvarchar(20) = null, 
	@vcDateShiftPlantId nvarchar(20) = null, @vcDate nvarchar(20) = null, @vcShiftId nvarchar(20) = null, @vcProdId nvarchar(20) = null, 
	@vcTrial nvarchar(20)= null, @vcAssTime nvarchar(20)= null, @vcBatch nvarchar(20)= null, @vcProdQty nvarchar(20)= null, @vcProRemark nvarchar(20)= null, 
	@vcMlICount nvarchar(20)= null, @vcParaSixteen nvarchar(20)= null, @vcMlMrp nvarchar(20)= null, @XML xml = null */
AS
BEGIN
	
	IF(@vcCase = '1')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcPlantId, vcPlantName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxPlant WHERE vcPlantId IN (SELECT vcPlantId FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxPlantAccessUsers WHERE vcEmpId = CAST(@vcParaTwo AS INT))
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '2')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcMachineId, vcMachineName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxMachine WHERE vcPlantId = CAST(@vcParaThree AS INT)
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '3')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcProductId, vcProductName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity WHERE vcMachineId = CAST(@vcParaFour AS INT) AND  btYsnActive = 1
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '4')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcBdCategoryId, vcBdCategory FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxBdCategory WHERE btActive = 1
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '5')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcBdCode, vcBdCode + ' - ' + vcBdReason vcBdRes FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxBdCode WHERE vcPlantId = CAST(@vcParaThree AS INT)
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '6')
	BEGIN
	SELECT  vcInternalMachineId , vcInternalMachineName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_IndxInterMachineName WHERE btYsnActive = 1 AND vcPlantId  = CAST(@vcParaThree AS INT)
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '7')
	BEGIN
	INSERT INTO noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction(vcUniqueIdPro, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, vcShiftId, vcPlantId, vcMachineId, vcProdId, vcTrial, vcAssignTime, vcBatch, vcProdQty, vcProRemark, vcMlICount, vcMlECount, vcMlMrp, vcInsertBy)
	SELECT @vcParaFive, @vcParaSix, @vcParaSeven, @vcParaEight, @vcParaThree, @vcParaFour, @vcParaNine, @vcParaTen, @vcParaEleven, @vcParaTwelve, @vcParaThirteen, @vcParaFourteen, @vcParaFifteen, @vcParaSixteen, @vcParaSeventeen, @vcParaTwo  
	END
	
	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '8')
	BEGIN
	DECLARE @tblXML TABLE ( intRowId int identity(1,1), vcUnqIdBd nvarchar(20), vcInMachineId nvarchar(10), vcBDCatId nvarchar(10), vcBDCod nvarchar(10), vcBdMin nvarchar(10), vcBdRemark nvarchar(300) )
	INSERT INTO @tblXML(vcUnqIdBd, vcInMachineId, vcBDCatId, vcBDCod, vcBdMin, vcBdRemark) Select stXML.Item.value('@strUnqIdBD[1]', 'varchar(20)'), stXML.Item.value('@strInMachineId[1]', 'varchar(50)'),
	stXML.Item.value('@strBDCatId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBDCod[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBdMin[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBdRemark[1]', 'varchar(300)') from @XML.nodes('//Item/List') as stXML(Item)
	INSERT INTO AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkBreakDown(vcUniqueIdBd, vcUniqueIdPro, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcInterMachineId, vcBDCatId, vcBDCod, vcBdMin, vcBdRemark, vcInsertBy)
	SELECT vcUnqIdBd, @vcParaFive, @vcParaSix, vcInMachineId, vcBDCatId, vcBDCod, vcBdMin, vcBdRemark, @vcParaTwo from @tblXML 
	--DROP TABLE #tblXML
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '9')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcUniqueIdPro, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, CASE WHEN vcShiftId= '1' THEN 'A' WHEN vcShiftId= '2' THEN 'B' WHEN vcShiftId= '3' THEN 'C' ELSE 'SHIFT' END AS vcShift, ISNULL(Ca.vcPlantName, 'No plant') AS vcPlant, Pr.vcPlantId, ISNULL(Ca.vcMachineName, 'No product') AS vcMachine, Pr.vcMachineId, ISNULL(vcProductName, 'No product') AS vcProduct, Pr.vcProdId, CASE WHEN vcTrial = '0' THEN 'No' WHEN  vcTrial = '1' THEN 'Yes' END AS vcTrial, vcAssignTime, vcBatch, vcProdQty, vcProRemark, vcMlICount, vcMlECount, vcMlMrp
	FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction Pr
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity Ca ON Pr.vcPlantId = Ca.vcPlantId AND Pr.vcMachineId = Ca.vcMachineId AND Pr.vcProdId = Ca.vcProductId
	WHERE vcDateShiftPlantId = @vcParaSix
	END


	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '10')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcUniqueIdBd, Bd.vcUniqueIdPro, Bd.vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, CASE WHEN vcShiftId= '1' THEN 'A' WHEN vcShiftId= '2' THEN 'B' WHEN vcShiftId= '3' THEN 'C' ELSE 'SHIFT' END AS vcShift, ISNULL(Ca.vcPlantName, 'No plant') AS vcPlant, Pr.vcPlantId, ISNULL(Ca.vcMachineName, 'No product') AS vcMachine, Pr.vcMachineId, ISNULL(vcProductName, 'No product') AS vcProduct, Pr.vcProdId, CASE WHEN vcTrial = '0' THEN 'No' WHEN  vcTrial = '1' THEN 'Yes' END AS vcTrial, vcInternalMachineName, vcInterMachineId, vcBdCategory, vcBDCatId, vcBdCode+ ' - ' + vcBdReason AS vcBdRes, vcBDCod, vcBdMin, vcBdRemark
	FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkBreakDown Bd
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction Pr ON Bd.vcUniqueIdPro = Pr.vcUniqueIdPro
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity Ca ON Pr.vcPlantId = Ca.vcPlantId AND Pr.vcMachineId = Ca.vcMachineId AND Pr.vcProdId = Ca.vcProductId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_IndxInterMachineName Im ON Bd.vcInterMachineId = Im.vcInternalMachineId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxBdCategory Bdc ON Bdc.vcBdCategoryId = Bd.vcBDCatId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxBdCode BCo ON BCo.vcBdCode = Bd.vcBDCod AND BCo.vcPlantId = Pr.vcPlantId
	WHERE Bd.vcDateShiftPlantId = @vcParaSix
	END
	
	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '11')
	BEGIN
	SELECT  SUM(CAST(vcAssignTime AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS vcAssignTime FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction WHERE vcDateShiftPlantId = @vcParaSix AND vcMachineId = @vcParaFour
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '12')
	BEGIN
	DELETE FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaFive
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '13')
	BEGIN
	DELETE FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkBreakDown WHERE vcUniqueIdBd = @vcParaFive
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '14')
	BEGIN
	UPDATE noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction SET vcMachineId = @vcParaFour, vcProdId = @vcParaNine, vcTrial = @vcParaTen, vcAssignTime = @vcParaEleven, vcBatch = @vcParaTwelve, vcProdQty = @vcParaThirteen, vcProRemark = @vcParaFourteen, vcMlICount = @vcParaFifteen, vcMlECount = @vcParaSixteen, vcMlMrp = @vcParaSeventeen WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaFive
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '15')
	BEGIN
	DECLARE  @tblXMLBD TABLE( intRowId int identity(1,1), vcUnqIdBd nvarchar(20), vcInMachineId nvarchar(10), vcBDCatId nvarchar(10), vcBDCod nvarchar(10), vcBdMin nvarchar(10), vcBdRemark nvarchar(300) )
	INSERT INTO @tblXMLBD(vcUnqIdBd, vcInMachineId, vcBDCatId, vcBDCod, vcBdMin, vcBdRemark) Select stXML.Item.value('@strUnqIdBD[1]', 'varchar(20)'), stXML.Item.value('@strInMachineId[1]', 'varchar(50)'),
	stXML.Item.value('@strBDCatId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBDCod[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBdMin[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBdRemark[1]', 'varchar(300)') 
	FROM @XML.nodes('//Item/List') as stXML(Item)
	UPDATE noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkBreakDown SET vcInterMachineId = vcInMachineId, vcBDCatId = x.vcBDCatId, vcBDCod = x.vcBDCod, vcBdMin = x.vcBdMin, vcBdRemark = x.vcBdRemark FROM @tblXMLBD x WHERE vcUniqueIdBd = x.vcUnqIdBd
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '16')
	BEGIN
	SELECT  SUM(CAST(vcAssignTime AS DECIMAL(12,2))) AS vcAssignTime FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkProduction WHERE vcUniqueIdPro != @vcParaFive AND vcDateShiftPlantId = @vcParaSix AND vcMachineId = @vcParaFour
	END


	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '17')
	BEGIN
	DECLARE  @tblXMLWast TABLE( intRowId int identity(1,1), vcUnqIdWaste nvarchar(30), vcWasteTypeId nvarchar(30), vcWasteId nvarchar(30), vcWastePurposeId nvarchar(30), vcWasteQuantity nvarchar(30), vcWasteWeightUnitId nvarchar(30) )
	INSERT INTO @tblXMLWast(vcUnqIdWaste, vcWasteTypeId, vcWasteId, vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity, vcWasteWeightUnitId) 
	Select stXML.Item.value('@strUnqIdWast[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastTypId[1]', 'varchar(50)'),stXML.Item.value('@strWastId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastPurpId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastQty[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastWUntId[1]', 'varchar(50)')
	FROM @XML.nodes('//Item/List') as stXML(Item)
	INSERT INTO noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo (vcUniqueIdWaste, vcUniqueIdPro, vcWastetypeId, vcWasteId, vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity, vcWasteWeightUnitId )
	SELECT vcUnqIdWaste, @vcParaTwo, vcWasteTypeId, vcWasteId, vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity, vcWasteWeightUnitId FROM @tblXMLWast
	
	END


	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '18')
	BEGIN
	SELECT  O.vcUniqueIdPro, T.vcUniqueIdWaste, O.vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, CASE WHEN vcShiftId= '1' THEN 'A' WHEN vcShiftId= '2' THEN 'B' WHEN vcShiftId= '3' THEN 'C' ELSE 'SHIFT' END AS vcShift, ISNULL(Ca.vcPlantName, 'No plant') AS vcPlant, O.vcPlantId, ISNULL(Ca.vcMachineName, 'No Machine') AS vcMachine, O.vcMachineId, ISNULL(vcProductName, 'No product') AS vcProduct, 
	vcProdId, CASE WHEN vcTrial = '0' THEN 'No' WHEN  vcTrial = '1' THEN 'Yes' END AS vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastageTypeName, vcWasteTypeId, vcWastageName, vcWasteId, vcWastagePurposeName, vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity, CASE WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '1' THEN 'Pc' WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '2' THEN 'Kg' END AS vcWasteWeightUnitNam
	FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne O 
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo T ON O.vcUniqueIdPro = T.vcUniqueIdPro
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity Ca ON O.vcPlantId = Ca.vcPlantId AND O.vcMachineId = Ca.vcMachineId AND O.vcProdId = Ca.vcProductId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageType WT ON T.vcWasteTypeId = WT.vcWastageTypeId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageName W ON T.vcWasteTypeId = W.vcWastageTypeId AND T.vcWasteId = W.vcWastageId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastagePurpose WP ON T.vcWastePurposeId = WP.vcWastagePurposeId
	WHERE O.vcDateShiftPlantId = @vcParaThree
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '19')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcWastageTypeId, vcWastageTypeName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageType WHERE vcPlantId = @vcParaThree
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '20')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcWastagePurposeId ,vcWastagePurposeName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastagePurpose WHERE vcPlantId = @vcParaThree
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '21')
	BEGIN
	SELECT vcWastageId, vcWastageName FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageName WHERE vcPlantId = @vcParaThree AND vcWastageTypeId = @vcParaFour
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '22')
	BEGIN
	INSERT INTO noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne (vcUniqueIdPro, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, vcShiftId, vcPlantId, vcMachineId, vcProdId, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcInsertBy)
	SELECT @vcParaTwo, @vcParaThree, @vcParaFour, @vcParaFive, @vcParaSix, @vcParaSeven, @vcParaEight, @vcParaNine, @vcParaTen, @vcParaEleven
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '23')
	BEGIN
	SELECT CAST(COUNT(*) AS VARCHAR(20)) AS vcRowCount FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne O LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo T ON O.vcUniqueIdPro = T.vcUniqueIdPro WHERE O.vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaThree
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '24')
	BEGIN
	DELETE FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne  WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaFour
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '25')
	BEGIN
	DELETE FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo  WHERE vcUniqueIdWaste = @vcParaFive
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '26')
	BEGIN
	DECLARE  @tblXMLWastUpdate TABLE( intRowId int identity(1,1), vcUnqIdPro nvarchar(30), vcUnqIdWaste nvarchar(30), vcMachineId nvarchar(30), vcProdId nvarchar(30), vcTrial nvarchar(3), vcBatch nvarchar(30), vcWasteTypeId nvarchar(30), vcWasteId nvarchar(30), vcWastePurposeId nvarchar(30), vcWasteQuantity nvarchar(30), vcWasteWeightUnitId nvarchar(30) )
	INSERT INTO @tblXMLWastUpdate(vcUnqIdPro, vcUnqIdWaste, vcMachineId, vcProdId, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWasteTypeId, vcWasteId, vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity, vcWasteWeightUnitId) 
	Select stXML.Item.value('@strUnqIdPro[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strUnqIdWast[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strMachineId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strProdId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strTrial[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strBatch[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastTypId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastPurpId[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastQty[1]', 'varchar(50)'), stXML.Item.value('@strWastWUntId[1]', 'varchar(50)')
	FROM @XML.nodes('//Item/List') as stXML(Item)
	UPDATE noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo  SET vcWasteTypeId = X.vcWasteTypeId, vcWasteId = X.vcWasteId, vcWastePurposeId = X.vcWastePurposeId, vcWasteQuantity = X.vcWasteQuantity, vcWasteWeightUnitId = X.vcWasteWeightUnitId FROM @tblXMLWastUpdate X  WHERE vcUniqueIdWaste = X.vcUnqIdWaste AND vcUniqueIdPro = X.vcUnqIdPro 
	UPDATE noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne SET vcMachineId = X.vcMachineId, vcProdId = X.vcProdId, vcTrial = X.vcTrial, vcBatch = X.vcBatch FROM @tblXMLWastUpdate X  WHERE  vcUniqueIdPro = X.vcUnqIdPro 
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '27')
	BEGIN
	CREATE  TABLE #tmp (intRowId INT IDENTITY(1,1), vcUniqueIdPro VARCHAR(20), vcUniqueIdWaste VARCHAR(20), vcDateShiftPlantId VARCHAR(20), vcDate VARCHAR(20), vcShift VARCHAR(20), vcPlant VARCHAR(20),  vcMachine  VARCHAR(20), vcProduct VARCHAR(200), vcTrial VARCHAR(20), vcBatch  VARCHAR(20), vcWastageType VARCHAR(150), vcWastageName  VARCHAR(150), vcWastagePurpose VARCHAR(150), vcWastageQty DECIMAL(10,2), vcWastWUnitNam VARCHAR(10) )
	INSERT INTO #tmp(vcUniqueIdPro, vcUniqueIdWaste, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, vcShift, vcPlant, vcMachine, vcProduct, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastageType, vcWastageName, vcWastagePurpose, vcWastageQty, vcWastWUnitNam)
	SELECT  O.vcUniqueIdPro, T.vcUniqueIdWaste, O.vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, CASE WHEN vcShiftId= '1' THEN 'A' WHEN vcShiftId= '2' THEN 'B' WHEN vcShiftId= '3' THEN 'C' ELSE 'SHIFT' END AS vcShift, ISNULL(Ca.vcPlantName, 'No plant') AS vcPlant, ISNULL(Ca.vcMachineName, 'No Machine') AS vcMachine, ISNULL(vcProductName, 'No product') AS vcProduct, 
	CASE WHEN vcTrial = '0' THEN 'No' WHEN  vcTrial = '1' THEN 'Yes' END AS vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastageTypeName, vcWastageName, vcWastagePurposeName, CAST(vcWasteQuantity AS DECIMAL(10,2)), CASE WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '1' THEN 'Pc' WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '2' THEN 'Kg' END AS vcWasteWeightUnitNam
	FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne O 
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo T ON O.vcUniqueIdPro = T.vcUniqueIdPro
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity Ca ON O.vcPlantId = Ca.vcPlantId AND O.vcMachineId = Ca.vcMachineId AND O.vcProdId = Ca.vcProductId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageType WT ON T.vcWasteTypeId = WT.vcWastageTypeId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageName W ON T.vcWasteTypeId = W.vcWastageTypeId AND T.vcWasteId = W.vcWastageId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastagePurpose WP ON T.vcWastePurposeId = WP.vcWastagePurposeId
	WHERE vcDate BETWEEN @vcParaFour AND @vcParaFive AND ISNULL(vcYsNAccept, '0') = '0' AND ISNULL(vcYsNCom, '0') = '0' AND ISNULL(vcYsNComSlv, '0') = '0'

	DECLARE @columns NVARCHAR(MAX), @sql NVARCHAR(MAX); SET @columns = N'';
	SELECT @columns+=N', p.'+QUOTENAME(vcWastageName) FROM (SELECT vcWastageName FROM #tmp AS p GROUP BY vcWastageName) AS x;

	SET @sql = N'SELECT vcUniqueIdPro Id, vcDate Date, vcShift Shift, vcMachine Machine, vcProduct Product, vcTrial Trial, vcBatch Batch, vcWastagePurpose Purpose, '+STUFF(@columns, 1, 2, '')+' FROM (SELECT vcUniqueIdPro, vcDate, vcShift, vcPlant, vcMachine, vcProduct, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastagePurpose, vcWastageQty, vcWastageName FROM #tmp) AS j PIVOT (SUM(vcWastageQty) 
	FOR vcWastageName in ('+STUFF(REPLACE(@columns, ', p.[', ',['), 1, 1, '')+')) AS p;';
	EXEC sp_executesql @sql

	DROP TABLE #tmp
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '28')
	BEGIN
	CREATE  TABLE #tmpC (intRowId INT IDENTITY(1,1), vcUniqueIdPro VARCHAR(20), vcUniqueIdWaste VARCHAR(20), vcDateShiftPlantId VARCHAR(20), vcDate VARCHAR(20), vcShift VARCHAR(20), vcPlant VARCHAR(20),  vcMachine  VARCHAR(20), vcProduct VARCHAR(200), vcTrial VARCHAR(20), vcBatch  VARCHAR(20), vcWastageType VARCHAR(150), vcWastageName  VARCHAR(150), vcWastagePurpose VARCHAR(150), vcWastageQty DECIMAL(10,2), vcWastWUnitNam VARCHAR(10) )
	INSERT INTO #tmpC(vcUniqueIdPro, vcUniqueIdWaste, vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, vcShift, vcPlant, vcMachine, vcProduct, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastageType, vcWastageName, vcWastagePurpose, vcWastageQty, vcWastWUnitNam)
	SELECT  O.vcUniqueIdPro, T.vcUniqueIdWaste, O.vcDateShiftPlantId, vcDate, CASE WHEN vcShiftId= '1' THEN 'A' WHEN vcShiftId= '2' THEN 'B' WHEN vcShiftId= '3' THEN 'C' ELSE 'SHIFT' END AS vcShift, ISNULL(Ca.vcPlantName, 'No plant') AS vcPlant, ISNULL(Ca.vcMachineName, 'No Machine') AS vcMachine, ISNULL(vcProductName, 'No product') AS vcProduct, 
	CASE WHEN vcTrial = '0' THEN 'No' WHEN  vcTrial = '1' THEN 'Yes' END AS vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastageTypeName, vcWastageName, vcWastagePurposeName, CAST(vcWasteQuantity AS DECIMAL(10,2)), CASE WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '1' THEN 'Pc' WHEN vcWasteWeightUnitId = '2' THEN 'Kg' END AS vcWasteWeightUnitNam
	FROM AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne O 
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageTwo T ON O.vcUniqueIdPro = T.vcUniqueIdPro
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxCapacity Ca ON O.vcPlantId = Ca.vcPlantId AND O.vcMachineId = Ca.vcMachineId AND O.vcProdId = Ca.vcProductId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageType WT ON T.vcWasteTypeId = WT.vcWastageTypeId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastageName W ON T.vcWasteTypeId = W.vcWastageTypeId AND T.vcWasteId = W.vcWastageId
	LEFT JOIN AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_indxWastagePurpose WP ON T.vcWastePurposeId = WP.vcWastagePurposeId
	WHERE ISNULL(vcYsNAccept, '0') = '0' AND ISNULL(vcYsNCom, '0') = '1' AND ISNULL(vcYsNComSlv, '0') = '0'

	DECLARE @columnsC NVARCHAR(MAX), @sqlC NVARCHAR(MAX); SET @columnsC = N'';
	SELECT @columnsC +=N', p.'+QUOTENAME(vcWastageName) FROM (SELECT vcWastageName FROM #tmpC AS p GROUP BY vcWastageName) AS x;

	SET @sqlC = N'SELECT vcUniqueIdPro Id, vcDate Date, vcShift Shift, vcMachine Machine, vcProduct Product, vcTrial Trial, vcBatch Batch, vcWastagePurpose Purpose, '+STUFF(@columnsC, 1, 2, '')+' FROM (SELECT vcUniqueIdPro, vcDate, vcShift, vcPlant, vcMachine, vcProduct, vcTrial, vcBatch, vcWastagePurpose, vcWastageQty, vcWastageName FROM #tmpC) AS j PIVOT (SUM(vcWastageQty) 
	FOR vcWastageName in ('+STUFF(REPLACE(@columnsC, ', p.[', ',['), 1, 1, '')+')) AS p;';
	EXEC sp_executesql @sqlC

	DROP TABLE #tmpC
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '29')
	BEGIN
	UPDATE AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne SET vcYsNAccept = '1', vcYsNComSlv = '0', vcYsNCom = '0' WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaTwo
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '30')
	BEGIN
	UPDATE AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne SET vcYsNAccept = '0', vcYsNComSlv = '0', vcYsNCom = '1' WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaTwo
	END

	ELSE IF(@vcCase = '31')
	BEGIN
	UPDATE AFBL_Factory.noncsd.FacTb_TrnsMilkWastageOne SET vcYsNAccept = '1', vcYsNComSlv = '1', vcYsNCom = '1' WHERE vcUniqueIdPro = @vcParaTwo
	END



	

END

	
GO
